original_title: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome - Day 6
overview: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome Night 6 took place in Tokyo, Japan on December 20, 2014. The main event was a six man tag featuring Hiroshi Tanahashi, Kota Ibushi & Togi Makabe taking on Kazuchika Okada, Shinsuke Nakamura & Tomohiro Ishii.
title: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome - Day 6
